N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 10 ยง 441.16 - Active medical staff

State Regulations

Hospital-based and nonhospital-based physicians, other
than interns and residents who are voting members of and can hold office in the
medical staff organization of the hospital. Notes
